pr_body: This pull request contains the project completed till this week.

### Summary of Changes

- Added the config for gh-pages to deploy the website.
- Setup GitHub actions for continuous build and deployment.
- Fixed broken links across the website.
- Setup pages for publications, people and about us.

pr_title: Added a test for build on a pull request
pr_body:
- In this PR i've fixed the build issues that occured in #5.
- Added a test which checks whether the site build is executing succesfully on a pull request.

- I noticed a bug which was causing the feature cards in the homepage to display in a different fashion. I have fixed this.
- There were a few redundant files, I have removed them as they will not be required in the future.
